</title>
<subSubSection id="CD7E13A1D64835699A92DA6C75D3122B" pageId="null" pageNumber="443" type="description">
<paragraph id="C57F305EC5A3A149743AA123FAFC0F7C" pageId="null" pageNumber="443">
20-120 cm hoch. Stengel meist 
<normalizedToken id="CA5928F35F123223B6F034396CD5E2DD" originalValue="mehrköpfig" pageId="null" pageNumber="443">mehrkoepfig</normalizedToken>
. 
<emphasis id="029299925C298ECDAF9C10F79D7A1B4B" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="443">
Blattabschnitte schmal lanzettlich, mit verdickten 
<normalizedToken id="8BCBE0C2FF443201A43302FFFE4C475B" originalValue="Rändern" pageId="null" pageNumber="443">Raendern</normalizedToken>
.
</emphasis>
<normalizedToken id="FEC6BD6E854E43A8DE3ECAD723D3A9FF" originalValue="Hülle" pageId="null" pageNumber="443">Huelle</normalizedToken>
1,6-2,0 cm lang und 1,3-1,6 cm dick. 
<emphasis id="E99DA7615A7EB3C6CE9D1954EEE0ED19" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="443">
<normalizedToken id="8A1396BC86E5017F090CFCBAE58E3178" originalValue="Anhängsel" pageId="null" pageNumber="443">Anhaengsel</normalizedToken>
der 
<normalizedToken id="A5242158AD3134DE5D38F28A3FF07C0D" originalValue="Hüllblätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="443">Huellblaetter</normalizedToken>
1
</emphasis>
- 
<emphasis id="143E0F2F42F8F66082706F350D93E870" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="443">
5 mm lang, den 
<normalizedToken id="83D8C9265F595B5DA232D354A21E38F7" originalValue="grünen" pageId="null" pageNumber="443">gruenen</normalizedToken>
Teil der 
<normalizedToken id="EA3F4FF499EFF2DF8D28740428BD5509" originalValue="Hüllblätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="443">Huellblaetter</normalizedToken>
nicht verdeckend
</emphasis>
(
<emphasis id="70D5BAE0F945DA7E8D609285D7230669" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="443">
der Kopf deshalb 
<normalizedToken id="E52098A7DD49273E97C0DD48BA40CE98" originalValue="grün" pageId="null" pageNumber="443">gruen</normalizedToken>
und schwarz gescheckt
</emphasis>
), 
<emphasis id="4A56EEBB277FBAAA16045AFD8007FD99" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="443">jederseits mit 5</emphasis>
- 
<emphasis id="CF55FDAB9FE3B08DA1D46E5CF2E14BB2" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="443">15, nur selten verzweigten, 1</emphasis>
- 
<emphasis id="40246373BABDEE03D0B9F7AE149C17EF" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="443">2 mm langen Fransen</emphasis>
und mit 0,2-0,5 mm breitem, herablaufendem Rand; 
<emphasis id="057DAEE970DCFEDC9FF77755E8001585" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="443">
ungeteiltes 
<normalizedToken id="E7F1F9A1D0EF5A6F269D7AD50157A261" originalValue="Mittelstück" pageId="null" pageNumber="443">Mittelstueck</normalizedToken>
</emphasis>
(von der Spitze des 
<normalizedToken id="17A3A7F04E075D69F3548C25E7803971" originalValue="grünen" pageId="null" pageNumber="443">gruenen</normalizedToken>
Teils bis zur Basis der Endfranse) 
<emphasis id="6CB700E8945BC22CE2AB5146287D7388" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="443">1</emphasis>
- 
<emphasis id="6FEBEA79DAF325D14A03885FC575D1DD" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="443">2</emphasis>
<normalizedToken id="7DF9B80D3DCD33E20A4712E943A01D83" originalValue="½" pageId="null" pageNumber="443">1/2</normalizedToken>
<emphasis id="43B5A451A989674C7D1350A340AD7F64" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="443">mal so lang wie breit.</emphasis>
<normalizedToken id="E40540F646DFEB403603A155E2729498" originalValue="Früchte" pageId="null" pageNumber="443">Fruechte</normalizedToken>
3,5-5 mm lang. - 
<normalizedToken id="5432E1A821390AE5414202A9DB13AB2C" originalValue="Blüte" pageId="null" pageNumber="443">Bluete</normalizedToken>
: Sommer.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="DE21C985F953CB1ADF94658E03EC039A" pageId="null" pageNumber="443">
<emphasis id="4376ACC0D1BCBDBABF7284F7C2DA6B9A" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="443">Zytologische Angaben. 2n</emphasis>
= 
<emphasis id="AFB7EA5AC880DA0759FBBDEC86C7C712" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="443">20:</emphasis>
Material aus Jugoslawien, 
<normalizedToken id="82F0BC003E722A4069C9A735A9832438" originalValue="zusätzlich" pageId="null" pageNumber="443">zusaetzlich</normalizedToken>
0-9 B-Chromosomen (
<normalizedToken id="01687C7F21D36A8868E8ED22EE4FC834" originalValue="Fröst" pageId="null" pageNumber="443">Froest</normalizedToken>
1958), aus Frankreich, 
<normalizedToken id="20630F716F49498DA28D4428A5B639E6" originalValue="zusätzlich" pageId="null" pageNumber="443">zusaetzlich</normalizedToken>
0-6 B-Chromosomen (Gardou 1969).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="FB1B66F1A167D7B4AC451B683882B088" pageId="null" pageNumber="443">
<emphasis id="F6491E9AD43ED5A009AF164C7CF27453" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="443">Standort.</emphasis>
Kollin, montan und subalpin. Trockene, steinige 
<normalizedToken id="3C00250CD7ADFF6255053ACEC289AF6A" originalValue="Böden" pageId="null" pageNumber="443">Boeden</normalizedToken>
in warmen Lagen. Trockenwiesen, Felsensteppen.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="04B077BF487125B1860A301EF209E5AF" pageId="null" pageNumber="443">
<emphasis id="158506E30D2AE2DED816DFB17880CA3D" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="443">
Verbreitung. Mi!tel- und 
<normalizedToken id="F78BF18A41CEFD865F5948FAF57671AD" originalValue="südeuropäische" pageId="null" pageNumber="443">suedeuropaeische</normalizedToken>
Gebirgspflanze
</emphasis>
(
<emphasis id="AE3E6C71B14A171B94945E4DCD99F06F" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="443">
<normalizedToken id="1F73D00E7A4618CBFDDE4FAAD4884CC3" originalValue="östlich" pageId="null" pageNumber="443">oestlich</normalizedToken>
</emphasis>
)
<emphasis id="F1C37CBD6145ED6FA22DBE7F398B4C37" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="443">:</emphasis>
Alpen, Jura, Gebirge der Balkanhalbinsel. - Im Gebiet: Jura mit 
<normalizedToken id="61DF7E3C9FA07B6D24C1F392C45E0CA9" originalValue="Vorgelände" pageId="null" pageNumber="443">Vorgelaende</normalizedToken>
, Hochrheingebiet, Hegau, zentral- und 
<normalizedToken id="728019CEB4167DD03CB056A4385C8921" originalValue="südalpine" pageId="null" pageNumber="443">suedalpine</normalizedToken>
<normalizedToken id="E5CFBCACD6E0CFF7BC1C158465B62329" originalValue="Täler" pageId="null" pageNumber="443">Taeler</normalizedToken>
; nicht 
<normalizedToken id="A27D12993890FB9581E01E9B09790953" originalValue="häufig" pageId="null" pageNumber="443">haeufig</normalizedToken>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="81EC66D720385CF87FC251321E93DC27" pageId="null" pageNumber="443">
<emphasis id="0816D3BF5279FDBD766C0BEFAB2542A0" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="443">Bemerkungen.</emphasis>
Pflanzen unter dem Namen 
<taxonomicName id="311B2FB1E89B5A6E27B9104E66B837F3" authority="Tratt., C. Fritschii Hayek" authorityName="Tratt., C. Fritschii Hayek" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Asteraceae" genus="Centaurea" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asterales" pageId="null" pageNumber="443" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="badensis">
<emphasis id="53A7183DE3C3A3B787260821CF3FBC55" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="443">C. badensis</emphasis>
Tratt., 
<emphasis id="1286F6A055D9B029DF63D84363F03ADE" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="443">C. Fritschii</emphasis>
Hayek
</taxonomicName>
und 
<taxonomicName id="7B2F5AFBEED3BFB0FB63521BC65666D8" authority="Reuter" authorityName="Reuter" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Asteraceae" genus="Centaurea" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asterales" pageId="null" pageNumber="443" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="grinensis">
<emphasis id="BA1295E51A536642205EC39973338B11" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="443">C. grinensis</emphasis>
Reuter
</taxonomicName>
werden hier in 
<taxonomicName id="40E50A3E9EE46F640D9E5BC19E1345FA" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Asteraceae" genus="Centaurea" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asterales" pageId="null" pageNumber="443" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="tenuifolia">
<emphasis id="D6554B5BDD43508B461C57FB7B9A75AB" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="443">C. tenuifolia</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
eingeschlossen.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
